procedure-definition.name: FL Student Assessment Data
procedure-definition.comment: The student assessments set consists of student assessments with date during the school year and related to assessment definitions with ids {"AP", "IB", "AICE"}.

procedure-definition.name: FL Industry Certification Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that participated in program "Career and Professional Academy" (FL-PGM-CAPE) on date during the school year. The courses include CTE courses that were scheduled for the student during the school year.

procedure-definition.name: FL Compensatory Project Evaluation Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that participated in program "Migrant" (FL-PGM-MIGRANT) on date during the school year. The student program participations set consists of student program participations related to "Migrant" (FL-PGM-MIGRANT) program that selected students participated during the school year.

procedure-definition.name: FL CTE Student Course Schedule Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that participated in program "Career and Technical Education" (FL-PGM-CTE) on date during the school year. The sections include all student's sections related to CTE courses (courses with not empty CTE Program Code) that were scheduled for the student during the school year.

procedure-definition.name: FL CTE Teacher Course Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: The sections include all teacher's sections related to CTE courses (courses with not empty CTE Program Code) that were scheduled for the teacher during the school year and for the students with CTE programs.

procedure-definition.name: FL Dropout Prevention Program Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes active students that participated in program "Dropout Prevention/Juvenile Justice Program" (FL-PGM-DROP) on date during the school year. All "Dropout Prevention/Juvenile Justice Program" participations of selected students during the school year are exported.

procedure-definition.name: FL English Language Learners Information Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that participated in program "English Language Learners" (FL-PGM-ELL) on date: 1) during selected survey period for periods 2 and 3 2) during the school year for period 5 To be reported "English Language Learners" student program participation should have ELL code in {"LY", "LF"}.

procedure-definition.name: FL Prior Student Status Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes active PK-12 students that were enrolled from the first day of the school year to the last day of: 1) the selected survey period for periods 2 and 3 2) the school year for survey period 5 Separate record is exported for each student enrollment span that overlaps with the dates range.

procedure-definition.name: FL Exceptional Student Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes avtive students that participated in program "Exceptional Student" (FL-PGM-EXCEPT) on date during: 1) the selected survey period for periods 1 - 4 2) the school year for survey period 5.

procedure-definition.name: FL Federal Indicator Status Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that have courses scheduled during: 1) the selected survey period for periods 2 and 3 2) the school year for survey period 5.

procedure-definition.name: FL Education Identifier Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that were active in current school year. If "Empty FLEID only" is checked, only students with not empty FL Education Identifier are extracted.

procedure-definition.name: FL Student Additional Funding Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that have assessments related to assessment definitions with ids in {"AP", "IB", "AICE"}.

procedure-definition.name: FL McKay Prepayment Verification Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that were active in current school year. The enrollment span of the student is latest enrollment span that has fisrt active date before snapshot date of the selected survey period.

procedure-definition.name: FL Teacher Course Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of teachers includes teachers that have sections for current school year that start before selected survey period (1, 2, 3 or 4) end date. The sections for the teacher include all sections for current school year that start before selected survey period (1, 2, 3 or 4) end date.

procedure-definition.name: FL Staff Additional Job Assignments Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of staff includes all active staff. The staff positions set of the staff includes staff positions that are: 1) not primary 2) active on selected survey period (2, 3).

procedure-definition.name: FL Student Course Transcript Information Data
FL Student Discipline Resultant Action Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of conduct actions includes actions with: 1) incident date that is on or between school year start date and: - the selected survey period end date for periods 2 and 3 - the school year end date for period 5 2) action code in {"C", "E", "F", "H", "I", "L", "M", "O", "P", "R", "S", "U"} 3) involvement type not in {"N", "U"}

procedure-definition.name: FL School Environmental Safety Incident Report Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of conduct incidents includes incidents with: 1) date between school year start date and: - the selected survey period end date for periods 2 and 3 - the school year end date for period 5 2) incident code in {"ARS", "BRK", "BUL", "DOC", "FIT", "HAR", "HAZ", "OMC", "PHA", "ROB", "SXH", "BAT", "HOM", "KID", "SXB", "ALC", "DRD", "DRU", "STL", "SXA", "SXO", "TBC", "TRE", "UBL", "UHR", "VAN", "WPO"}

procedure-definition.name: FL Student End of Year Status Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that were active in current school year. The enrollment span of the student is latest enrollment span that has fisrt active date before snapshot date of survey period 5.

procedure-definition.name: FL Staff Professional Development Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected staff set includes all active staff. The professional development plans of the staff are all professional development plans with renewal date on or after the school year start date.

procedure-definition.name: FL Student Course Schedule Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students that were active in current school year. The sections include all student's sections that were scheduled for the student during the selected survey period (1-4).

procedure-definition.name: FL Student Demographic Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes active students for survey periods: 6 - with grade levels KG-12 8 - with grade level "KG" or with grade level 03-12 who participating in the Progress Monitoring and Reporting Network (PMRN) 9 - who participated "Neglected/Delinquent" or "Title I Supplemental Educational Services" during the survey period

procedure-definition.name: FL Staff Demographic Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected staff set includes all active staff.

procedure-definition.name: FL Staff Experience Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected staff set includes all active staff. One record per experience type of the staff is extracted. Existance of experience type is determined based on: 1) not empty experience type length or 2) staff position that is actual on the selected survey period and that contains the experience type.

procedure-definition.name: FL Title I Supplemental Educational Services Data
procedure-definition.comment: For survey periods 3 selected set of students includes students that participated in program "Title I Supplemental Educational Services" (FL-PGM-SES) on date during the selected survey period. For survey periods 5 and 9 selected set of students includes students that participated in program "Title I Supplemental Educational Services" (FL-PGM-SES) on date during the school year.

procedure-definition.name: FL Student Transportation Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students with assigned transportations that were active during the selected survey period (1-4).

procedure-definition.name: FL WDIS AGE Student Course Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students in membership in an Adult Basic or Adult Secondary Education course and AGE program at any time during the relevant reporting period (F, G, W, X, S).

procedure-definition.name: FL WDIS AGE Test Record Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of student assessments includes assessments for each pre- or post-tests taken by an adult general education student at any time prior to and during the relevant reporting period (F, W, S).

procedure-definition.name: FL WDIS CTE Student Course Schedule Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes students in membership in postsecondary career and technical education courses and CTE program in which students were in membership at any time during the relevant reporting period (F, G, W, X, S).

procedure-definition.name: FL WDIS Student Demographic Information Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes any postsecondary career and technical education and adult general education students reported on any other WDIS reporting format for the survey period (F, G, W, X, S).

procedure-definition.name: FL WDIS Student End of Term Status Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Selected set of students includes any postsecondary career and technical education and adult general education students reported on any other WDIS reporting format for the survey period (F, W, S).

procedure-definition.name: FL WDIS Supplemental Information Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Records include PS CTE and AGE students with not empty Additional Hours Credited and CAPE programs for the survey period (F, W, S).

procedure-definition.name: FL WDIS Teacher Course Export Data
procedure-definition.comment: Records include PS CTE and AGE sections for the survey period (F, W, S).
